00:30:02.660 --> 00:30:08.080 position:56%
of ReadersFirst to open up ebook
content and provide interoperability

00:30:08.080 --> 00:30:10.970
between those platforms
so that you can serve it

00:30:10.970 --> 00:30:13.060
in a library-owned environment.

00:30:13.060 --> 00:30:15.680
So Michael Blackwell who's
in the fourth row here,

00:30:15.680 --> 00:30:18.720
you want to give a wave, has I
think been one of many leaders

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:23.270 position:56%
that have stepped up, and are really
helping to rejuvenate or double-down

00:30:23.270 --> 00:30:27.580
on ReadersFirst, and the promise
