00:30:27.580 --> 00:30:29.950
And I think that both
Greg and Christine hit

00:30:29.950 --> 00:30:33.830
on something very powerful which
is the idea that our, you know,

00:30:33.830 --> 00:30:37.360
while we are small institutions
