importance of interoperability.

00:36:28.510 --> 00:36:32.440 position:56%
And even if it's going to take your
library another year or two or three

00:36:32.440 --> 00:36:36.640
to roll out these platforms you
can help right now by underscoring

00:36:36.640 --> 00:36:41.320
with your budget to your vendors
the importance of interoperability,

00:36:41.320 --> 00:36:44.900 position:56%
philosophically, fundamentally which
will do nothing but open options

00:36:44.900 --> 00:36:47.430
for you as a library
and for other libraries.

00:36:47.430 --> 00:36:50.450
And to Greg's survey and the
point about the financial power

00:36:50.450 --> 00:36:55.020
of libraries, even just
within the 20 partners named

00:36:55.020 --> 00:36:58.510
