00:37:01.880 --> 00:37:03.450
So it is a substantial market.

00:37:03.450 --> 00:37:05.660
And we are spending a lot of money.

00:37:05.660 --> 00:37:07.840
And so if we can speak
with a unified voice

00:37:07.840 --> 00:37:09.870
about what we want we
can change that market.

00:37:09.870 --> 00:37:12.260
And we can start saying
to our vendors

00:37:12.260 --> 00:37:14.550
that interoperability
is table steaks.

00:37:14.550 --> 00:37:17.030
It's not an extra, it
is what we require.

00:37:17.030 --> 00:37:19.960
When we buy content it's ours and
we want the ability and the right

00:37:19.960 --> 00:37:23.480 position:56%
to serve it in the best environment
for our users, and in an environment

00:37:23.480 --> 00:37:25.050
